  <title>Create a Subsystem</title>

  <p>The below steps demonstrates on how to create a subsystem using <gui>Apx GUI</gui>:</p>
  <list>
    <item><p>Click on the <gui>+</gui>button in the top left corner.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click on the <gui>New Subsystem</gui> button.</p></item>
    <item><p>Choose the <gui>Stack</gui> to be used for the Subsystem from the available list.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click on the <gui>Create</gui> button to pull the image and create a Subsystem container.</p></item>
    <item><p>After creating the Subsystem, click on the Console icon in bottom right corner to start working.</p></item>
  </list>

  <figure>
        <title>Apx GUI Subsystem Creation Panel</title>
        <media type="image" its:translate="no" src="media/apx-gui-create-subsystems.png"/>
  </figure>

    <p>The created Subsystem can be reset and removed by navigating to it and then pressing on the <gui>Delete Package Manager</gui> button.</p>

